node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'O Richard Yu @richardyuzee 5 biggest mistakes I made as a beginner entrepreneur...'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 1. Lack of consistency. Your success will NEVER exceed your habits, and I had inconsistent sleep times, diet, and work times.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 2. Porn Addiction. Super vulnerable here, but struggled with this for YEARS (99% of guys do), and never took ownership over this.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 3. Shiny Object Syndrome. I failed 4 businesses before I succeeded with my 5th because was constantly chasing new business after new business.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 4.1 cared more about money than impact. just wanted to hustle and make money and lost sight of the whole point of entrepreneurship. To ADD VALUE to the lives of others, and as a result of that, you make money.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 5. Lack of congruency with my faith in God. I went to church, read the Bible, and "looked" like I was a person of faith, but my heart and actions didn't align with it. The second started to do things for God, my business skyrocketed.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee So those are the biggest mistakes I regret making when I first started in business. If you're serious about your success, avoid these at all cost.'.
